  <brief_title>Myocardial Protection and Clinical Outcome in Patients Undergoing Tetralogy of Fallot Repair : A Randomized Study of Two Different Cardioplegia Technique</brief_title>
  <acronym>TOF</acronym>
  <official_title>MYOCARDIAL PROTECTION AND CLINICAL OUTCOME IN PATIENTS UNDERGOING TETRALOGY OF FALLOT REPAIR: A RANDOMIZED STUDY OF TWO CARDIOPLEGIC TECHNIQUES</official_title>
